# Committed test fixture (see .gitignore's `!.env.test` exception) — not a
# secret. Vite auto-loads .env.[mode], and vitest's default mode is 'test',
# so these values back Consent.test.tsx's "renders real policy/offer links"
# assertions without needing a real production URL.
VITE_POLICY_URL=https://stasis.example/policy
VITE_OFFER_URL=https://stasis.example/offer
